A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Excess Ownership of Single–Family Residences Excise Tax
3 (End Hedge Fund Control of Maryland Homes Act of 2025)
4 FOR the purpose of imposing an excise tax on the acquisition and excess ownership of
